The ONS colour palette is available to services using the design system so pages and elements look consistent and coherent.

Our text and background colours are designed to meet accessibility needs. We aim for {{
    onsExternalLink({
        "url": "https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/#visual-audio-contrast-contrast",
        "linkText": "WCAG AA compliance"
    })
}} contrast as far as possible. Read more about [accessibility and colour](#colour-contrast) on this page.

