## Colour contrast
Contrast between foreground and background colours are tested to ensure {{
    onsExternalLink({
        "url": "https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/#visual-audio-contrast-contrast",
        "linkText": "WCAG AA compliance"
    })
}}. Where colour is used to draw attention to an item (e.g. [panel](/components/panel)) and insufficient contrast exists between a background colour and element colour, additional techniques may be required to provide support for users unable to perceive the colour.

